node.text:
So you've probably heard that Cyberpunk 2077 dropped last night but did you know you could win the real life car from the game?? Thanks to my friends at @rockstarenergy this epic build dubbed the Quadra could be yours. All you have to do is purchase one of the special Cyberpunk x Rockstar edition cans, crack the tab and enter the code at www.2077.rockstarenergy.com. 

Don't miss your shot at this build by the rad dudes at the @therockstargarage here in Southern California. 

@mrnicashby @therockstargarage @rockstarenergy 

#rockstarenergy #cyberpunk2077#Quadra#rockstargarage#giveaway

node.text: Huge thanks to @ToyotaUSA for dropping off the brand new #Corolla Apex! I had the pleasure of being one of the first to test drive this beauty on the streets of LA. Lots of awesome features like the Black and Bronze body kit, 18" flow formed wheels, lowered track tuned suspension, a fresh bronze stitched interior and more 💪🏼. Check it out. #ad  #LetsGoPlaces

node.text: The only track time the #EastCoastCar has seen all year and it only did half a lap 🤦🏼‍♂️. Things have been BUSY! Looking forward to buttoning this car up with some fresh @rotiform’s, wrap from @newschoolvinyl, alignment, and hitting some @lockcitydrift_ events this fall 🤘🏼 #RT411

node.text: We had some fun at the #NHdrifthouse with the @gumout team in the latest episode of #BlackOut 🤘🏼 Link in profile. #RT411

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ryan Tuerck in Indianapolis Motor Speedway with @teamtoyota, @toyotaracing, and @toyota_trd. May be an image of motorcycle and outdoors.

node.text: Dirt Midgets rule! Had such a good time trying to wheel these things. Drifting on dirt as fast as you possibly can? Yes please! I did my best but needed more time to get comfortable. Some early entry drifting tendencies were not helping me. Massive thank you to @toyotaracing for the experience and @cannonmac_08 for doing your best to coach me. Would love to do this again 🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻

node.text: Today is going to be rad! Massive thanks to @toyotaracing for the opportunity. Seat swap competition with Dirt Midgets 🤘🏼 400 HP naturally aspirated pushrod  4 Cylinders.
